property.value: Instructions for running this example: 1. Set the file parameter of the FormattedLineReader. The file is located in the directory of this demo and called formatted_input_data.txt. 2. Compile the c code located in the directory of this demo in the subfolder "ccode" into a library. 3. Set the parameter of "CCodeLibrary" to the name of the library. 4. Run this example with the updated library path
